                                "byte_start": 80912,
                                "byte_stop": 115185,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 86-761, Forrester against White will be announced by Justice O\u0027Connor."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.562,
                        "stop": 96.94,
                        "byte_start": 115185,
